---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Privacy Policy — Sylvelle"
  description="Sylvelle's privacy policy. Short version: we collect nothing."
>
  <Header />
  <main class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 py-20">

    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h1 class="font-display text-4xl tracking-widest text-ink mb-4">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <div class="mx-auto h-px w-12 bg-copper opacity-60"></div>
      <p class="font-body text-sm text-ink/50 mt-4">Last updated: June 2026</p>
    </div>

    <div class="prose-sylvelle space-y-8 font-body text-ink/70 leading-relaxed text-sm">

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-heading text-xl text-ink mb-3">The short version</h2>
        <p>
          Sylvelle collects nothing. No analytics, no advertising identifiers, no crash reports,
          no behavioural tracking. Every piece of data you enter stays on your device, encrypted
          by a passphrase only you know. We have no server to send it to even if we wanted to.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-heading text-xl text-ink mb-3">Data we collect</h2>
        <p>
          <strong>None.</strong> The app does not communicate with any server operated by us.
          It does not transmit usage data, crash reports, device identifiers, or any personal
          information.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-heading text-xl text-ink mb-3">Data stored on your device</h2>
        <p>
          All data you enter — journal entries, measurements, task progress, coaching preferences,
          and any photos or voice clips — is stored exclusively on your device. It is encrypted
          using AES-256 (SQLCipher for the database, AES-GCM for media files), secured by a
          passphrase you choose. We cannot access it under any circumstances.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-heading text-xl text-ink mb-3">Optional AI coach</h2>
        <p>
          If you choose to enable the optional AI coach, you provide your own API key from a
          third-party AI provider (such as OpenAI or a compatible service). Requests made through
          the AI coach are sent directly from your device to that provider, under their own
          privacy policy. We do not see or store these requests.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-heading text-xl text-ink mb-3">Permissions</h2>
        <p>The app may request the following device permissions:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-1 mt-2">
          <li><strong>Camera</strong> — used only for in-app photo journaling. Photos are encrypted immediately and never saved to your camera roll.</li>
          <li><strong>Microphone</strong> — used only for the voice trainer feature. Clips are encrypted on capture and stored locally.</li>
          <li><strong>Biometrics / fingerprint</strong> — used as a convenient layer over your passphrase lock. Biometrics never replace the passphrase and can be disabled.</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-3">All permissions are optional and can be revoked at any time in your device settings.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-heading text-xl text-ink mb-3">Third-party services</h2>
        <p>
          Sylvelle does not integrate any third-party analytics, advertising, or tracking SDKs.
          This website uses no cookies and no tracking scripts.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-heading text-xl text-ink mb-3">Children and the Teen Edition</h2>
        <p>
          The Teen Edition is designed for users aged 13–17 and carries the same no-collection
          policy. No data about minor users is transmitted anywhere.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-heading text-xl text-ink mb-3">Contact</h2>
        <p>
          Questions about this policy? Reach us on
          <a href="https://instagram.com/sylvelle" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-copper hover:underline">
            Instagram @sylvelle
          </a>.
        </p>
      </section>

    </div>

  </main>
  <Footer />
</Layout>
